<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hehpihna Kuong chuh a kalto tai,
 Isu'n Van lampi chuh A siem tai;
 A dogal a-sang-a-za A zo,
 Hun pui ina Van chung gam nuomah.

[V2]
 Gam nuoma um dingin (2)
 Lam dik lamah hung-un-u-leh-nau,
 Gam nuom um dingin (2)
 Lam dik lamah hung-un-u-leh-nau.

[V3]
 2. Zie gam chuh manlo in chang hitiu,
 Aman ei lungsiet nasat ziekin;
 Bangdi'n em ginglo a I um ding?
 Gingin, hung mai tau uo u-leh-nau.

[V4]
 3. Hehpihna Kuong chuh tuhin chieh leh,
 Hung kileh kit puona sam leng le;
 Zion gam nuom zuonin chieh tana,
 Nang kap ta'n la tuisanglien galah.

[V5]
 4. Isu'n lainat in A hun sam ie,
 Ginglote hawn gingin hun zuon un;
 Tichun lungsietna Kuong hum un lau,
 Pathien lungsietna gam tunna ding.</lyrics>
<title>THE WAY OF HEAVEN</title>
<hymn_number>237</hymn_number>
</song>